{"tid":796644,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩佬：我不認為是艱難時刻","createTime":"2018-08-28T02:06:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T02:28:02.000Z","uid":153600,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"00862720be9eab4e11fb747cc4eaa9c75ccb626c","tid":796644,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:06:29.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Mtxf%2FLmfa2MhPr1aEs7il57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=bfe16ee4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯主場吞了熱刺3蛋，主帥摩連奴卻認為球員的表現令他高興，不認為球隊處於艱難時刻。<br />\n<br />\n「最好的一隊、進取並施壓的一隊，製造了機會而錯失了，熱刺首個角球就製造了1個入球，即時入局。我感到懊惱，但我為球員及表現感到開心。」摩連奴賽後說。<br />\n<br />\n「我們今天所創造的機會比之前大部份比賽都要多，所以我當然感到懊惱。球迷是最好的足球判官，他們對球員很好。己隊不敵西維爾（去季歐聯16強）後被柴台，因為我們活該。今天在主場輸波，球員離場時得到掌聲，因為他們配得，所以我們會保持嘗試、嘗試、嘗試。」<br />\n<br />\n「我不認為這是一個艱難的時刻。」曼聯3戰1勝2負得3分，但摩佬賽後顯然看重表現多於戰果。"},{"pid":"f93e0460be830a1c182cd518e9259748af48ae16","tid":796644,"uid":4139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:22:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"> 但摩佬賽後顯然看重表現多於戰果。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100bca419a986c69fc7e025149d8ea11b63d300c","tid":796644,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:24:59.000Z","msg":"最中意季初輸得肉酸,之後後上封皇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c29d56ca53eebbc27666daeced1aff2758966ff","tid":796644,"uid":45428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:25:32.000Z","msg":"又有得出街食飯 爽呀"},{"pid":"9b6c0e936e98134a6d988f97422cf028dad02f46","tid":796644,"uid":69614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:28:02.000Z","msg":"日日投訴無買人<br />\n轉頭俾隊無買人嘅作客大炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}